001package com.technototes.path.util;
002
003/**
004 * IMU axes signs in the order XYZ (after remapping).
005 */
006public enum AxesSigns {
007    PPP(0b000),
008    PPN(0b001),
009    PNP(0b010),
010    PNN(0b011),
011    NPP(0b100),
012    NPN(0b101),
013    NNP(0b110),
014    NNN(0b111);
015
016    public final int bVal;
017
018    AxesSigns(int bVal) {
019        this.bVal = bVal;
020    }
021}
